                "invention-title": [
                    "Hydrogen energy locomotive ventilation system, control method and device and related equipment",
                    "氢能源机车通风系统、控制方法、装置及相关设备"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a hydrogen energy locomotive ventilation system, a control method and device and related equipment, and relates to the technical field of hydrogen energy locomotives. The ventilation system comprises a ventilation device used for ventilating a hydrogen storage room of the hydrogen energy locomotive; the time-delay switch circuit is connected between a first power supply circuit of the hydrogen energy locomotive and a second power supply circuit of the ventilation device, and is used for switching from an off state to a closed state under the condition that the first power supply circuit is switched on, and then switching to the off state after a preset duration, and the time-delay switch circuit is switched off under the condition that the time-delay switch circuit is in the on state. The second power supply circuit is in a conducting state; and the control device is connected with the second power supply circuit and is used for controlling the second power supply circuit to be in an on or off state after the time delay switch circuit is switched from the on state to the off state. According to the ventilation system, the risk hidden danger caused by hydrogen leakage of the hydrogen energy source locomotive is reduced, and reliable guarantee is provided for safe operation of the hydrogen energy source locomotive."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本公开提供了一种氢能源机车通风系统、控制方法、装置及相关设备，涉及氢能源机车技术领域。该通风系统包括：通风装置，用于对氢能源机车的储氢间进行通风；延时开关电路，连接于氢能源机车的第一供电电路和通风装置的第二供电电路之间，用于在第一供电电路导通的情况下，从断开状态切换为闭合状态，且持续预设时长后，再切换为断开状态，其中，延时开关电路处于导通状态的情况下，第二供电电路处于导通状态；控制装置，与第二供电电路连接，用于在延时开关电路从闭合状态切换为断开状态后，控制第二供电电路处于导通或断开状态。本公开通过提出的通风系统，降低了氢能源机车氢气泄漏带来的风险隐患，为氢能源机车的安全运行提供了可靠保障。"
                }
            ]
